               <msContents>
                  <summary>Four Gospels EMML: Matthew, fol. 10r-46r; Mark, fol. 47r-69r; Luke, fol. 71r-107v; John, fol. 108r-139v. EMIP: Four Gospels, አርባዕቱ፡ ወንጌል፡  Pp. 1-2: List of 68 sections of the Gospel of Matthew. Pp. 3-18: Introduction to the four gospels, with the Eusebian canon lists. Pp. 19-91: Matthew. Pp. 91-92: List of 48 sections of the Gospel of Mark. Pp. 93-137: Gospel of Mark. Pp. 138-139: List of the 80 sections of the Gospel of Luke. Pp. 141-214: Gospel of Luke. P. 214: List of 19 sections of the Gospel of John. Pp. 215-278: Gospel of John. </summary>
                  
                  
               </msContents>
